fields.short_description_en:
Our achievements

Over the past 5 years, i.e. In 2016-2021, in the specified specialty, the department issued 5 teaching aids (RUMS MES RK), 40 teaching aids, 6 virtual practical works, 6 video lectures, more than 100 scientific and methodological articles and 64 acts of implementation in the educational process.

In the 2018-2019 and 2019-2020 academic years, as a result of the Republican Student Subject Olympiad in the specialties "Vocational Training" and "Fine Arts and Drawing" they took the honorable 3rd place.

Every year we participate in the Republican student competition among universities. In the 2018-2019, 2019-2020 academic years they took the honorable 3rd place, and in the 2020-2021 academic year they took the 2nd honorary place.

Currently, on the basis of the department, higher professional education operates according to a two-step system:

5В012000 (6В01405) - "Pedagogy of technical and vocational education" (bachelor's degree);

5В010700 (6В01404) - "Artistic work and design" (bachelor's degree);

5В010600 (6В01403) - "Music Education" (bachelor's degree);

6М012000 (7М01420) - "Pedagogy of vocational education" (Master's degree);

Currently, in the 2020-2021 academic year, 16 undergraduates are studying at the department.

In March 2018, on the basis of the department, a gallery of fine and decorative-applied arts was opened. In the gallery of fine and decorative-applied arts monthly exhibitions of students and teachers of the department of "Professional education and art" are exhibited. In the 2020-2021 academic year, exhibitions of students in the specialty "Fine Arts and Drawing" were held Orazbay Nauryzbay and Orakbay Gaukhar.

